How do I calculate the figures for a 10,000 ton Orion? Could I simply multiply Mauk2's results for a 2000 ton Orion by five? Just curious about how the number of SRB's for a bigger Orion would be worked out. Is fuel efficiency influenced by total mass or is it a straight graph of fuel to mass? <br>
